Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dresden...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,wait in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, give me the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cedok Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Three frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my father said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If the monster you're chasing is a twin...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Their mother is alive and is living in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:29.54,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,400)\pos(360,340)}Grimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going, Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find the material you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After the unification of East and West Germany,\Nthis institutions works completely changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so those are the only hooks we have from before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for causing you so much\Ntrouble, Director Galbreckt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare for this much to be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the Berlin Wall was destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the dangerous material in the East has been disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing for certain is that there were cases\Nof child abuse in East German orphanages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's still hard to find materials to even prove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The orphanages in East German were normally under the jurisdiction of the Ministry of Public Welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem was for the children whose parents were criminals, anarchists, spies, illegal immigrants,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and those with no influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children were cared for at Kinderheim,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which was under the jurisdiction of the Ministry of Internal Affairs, which was known for its bad reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know exactly how far the abuse and brainwashing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that occurred in that special orphanage went.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thoroughly investigate what exactly\Ntook place inside that orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoroughly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's quite an investigation you're undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The government employees are probably covering\Nfor each other, or at least won't rat the others out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Including a certain Mr. Schunua, who's employed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Schunua?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an educator at 62 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked him for an interview, but he declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You should keep a lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the unification, Dr. Schunua might\Nhave participated in child abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I make copies of these books?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer, you're a journalist\Nfrom West Germany, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm from this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked at a paper in Leipzig.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never have thought that a protector of\Nhuman rights would be from the East side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,back then I flew all over the world as a correspondent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got missions from the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What a large bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's full of the papers I've collected\Nthroughout East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll expect a great newspaper article from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you off to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prague, Czechoslovakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They were picking on you pretty bad back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So they ended up taking your shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,People can live without shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all born barefoot anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,those who would bully others and take away their shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't let losers like them make you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Too big for you to walk in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.23,Names,,0,0,40,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}Dresden Station
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The bag with my passport in it was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your passport?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to see my sister in Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got word that she collapsed yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to make it there as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already tried that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, my sister doesn't have\Nmoney to pay for her doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The bag that was stolen also had my wallet in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I can't go to see her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I could at least send her some money,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't even do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I don't need that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could just get enough money to see\Nher at the hospital, that'd be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all I can give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Danke Schoen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Write your address for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as your sister gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave your money to him so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious it was all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always around this station looking for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't let them trick you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was tricked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Express line to Prague will be leaving Platform 7 at 3:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Japanese, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Konnichiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been to Japan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 1982.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a lot of wiretaps and high-tech gadgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And this song was popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"At the north cemetery road."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"At the north....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,bar road."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"At the north bar road."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there were the robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought one of the plastic models for\Nmy kid. He absolutely loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your son now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll have to take a look at your passports.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Danke Schoen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elba River.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how the trout are doing this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year I caught one about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you'd be able to this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Danke Schoen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your secret's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They know that passport's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get out of here, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the border patrol knows about your fake passport\Nand they're going to come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get out of here, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My bag was so big, I got stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Very important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happened to the man who was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an Asian man in this\Nroom with you, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he went to the dining car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You, check that car over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an emergency in passenger car 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,An Asian man had a fake passport!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the emergency brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't chase you this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The train stopped, so I got off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't introduced myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd let me, can I guide you to the border, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this area well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I come here to fish often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The climbing is a little difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but the scenery is a sight to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked at a newspaper back when there was a East and West Germany,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,although I'm a freelance journalist now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read all the articles about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There were false charges made\Nall the time in East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This political prisoner was falsely accused.\NThat murderer was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing that all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can identify real criminals from\Nthe ones who are falsely accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you to stop calling me Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're an excellent brain surgeon,\Naren't you, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a doctor anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice view!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, we can see whoever's trying to follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have wine, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and some delicious cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't have that much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is still high in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to cross the border when it's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Picnics sure are fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to have one occasionally, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Having such beautiful surroundings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and delicious food...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the times that you feel happy to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I respect doctors like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Journalists like me might give people a\Nlittle happiness if I write a good article,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but you... you can give people life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Last month in Munich,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot someone for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:18:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Before then my hands trembled and I couldn't aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But after I shot him once,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,my hands stopped trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,from here on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there is another person I have to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I come to the Elba River to fish, I think to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could have come here fishing with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dead son?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can catch a trout this big here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He died without ever knowing the joy of fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If a doctor like you were near him back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,his life would have been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, I caught a fish this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After you cross that mountain,\Nyou'll be at the Czech border.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When you pass through that, you'll reach a wooded road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be able to catch a ride there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head back to the station now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You really helped me, Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pray for your good fortune,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ever meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,let's have another picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is burdened with sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Those sins will never disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,there are still things that you must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:42.30,Names,,0,0,40,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}Prague, Czechoslovakia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is absolutely beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've been here, but Prague seems\Nlike a town right out of a fairy tale at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally in love with this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Mr. Petrov, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought your Russian nationality and\Nhave been living in Czechoslovakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help me, Mr. Petrov?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I should call you Mr. Reinhart Biermann?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a special orphanage in East Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an experimentation ground for brainwashing\Nyoung boys and changing their personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was called 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the director there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}were{\i0} the director there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,back there in East Berlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,at 511 Kinderheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Gazing at what is known now in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:23:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Your eyes believe in kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of purity...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.45,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Ghost of 511
